These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, lavender
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
2. the person who likes pink is not to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Color        | pink   | lavender   |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
City: venice, london
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, software-developer
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the person traveling to london##8
2. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| City   | london | venice   |
| Job      | software-developer | project-manager |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, singing
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, motorbike
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Hobby          | singing | collecting |
| Transport   | subway   | motorbike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
