.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-7::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, pall-mall
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, february
1. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
2. the pall-mall-smoker is not to the right of the pall-mall-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |
| Cigar    | dunhill    | pall-mall |
| Birthday   | february | july       |

