.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-8::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, apple
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee
1. the person eating cabbage is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
2. the person eating apple is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |
| Food         | apple | cabbage |
| Beverage   | 7up   | coffee   |

