.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, december
2 different pets are kept: frog, bird
1. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
2. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Birthday      | june      | december |
| Pet   | frog | bird  |

 